    "instruction": "Build a URL containing query parameters as plain text. Preserve the special characters with appropriate escaping, verify the URL with show, and report it.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]$url = str \"https://example.com/search?query=DSL\\\\&page=2\"\n[CODE]show $url\n[RESULT]https://example.com/search?query=DSL\\&page=2\nThe request URL is $url.",
    "output_json": {
      "url": "https://example.com/search?query=DSL\\&page=2",
