    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import robot1\n[CODE]$env = tensor robot1_scan()\n[CODE]$plan = tensor robot1_model($env)\n[CODE]robot1_act($plan)\n[EXCEPTION]robot1_exception: Flood risk detected.\n[COMMENT]Deploy the emergency waterproof cover and retreat to higher ground before water reaches critical components.\n[CODE]show robot1_error_router_determine()\n[RESULT]flood_retreat\n[CODE]$recovery = tensor robot1_environment_error_recovery()\nThe robot deployed its waterproof cover and safely retreated to higher ground.\n[CODE]return \"Recovered\"",
