    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import robot1\n[CODE]$coop = tensor robot1_scan()\n[CODE]$plan = tensor robot1_model($coop)\n[CODE]robot1_act($plan)\n[EXCEPTION]robot1_exception: Partner wheel locked.\n[COMMENT]Synchronize with the stopped partner and prevent dragging the shared load.\n[CODE]show robot1_error_router_determine()\n[RESULT]sync_stop\n[CODE]$recovery = tensor robot1_cooperation_error_recovery()\nThe robot synchronized with its partner and safely stopped while supporting the load.\n[CODE]return \"Recovered\"",
